OL,3,CCalls from the Channel Islands to
OL,4,Callow bluefin tuna fishing
OL,6,Fand fishing industries are calling for
OL,7,Frules around bluefin tuna to be
OL,8,Frelaxed.
OL,10,FBluefin tuna were previously facing
OL,11,Fextinction and under current laws,
OL,12,Ffishing the species is prohibited due
OL,13,Fto dwindling stock.
OL,15,FBut now that the species is no longer
OL,16,Fendangered, Guernsey States are
OL,17,Fexploring lifting the ban, with many
OL,18,Fin Jersey calling for similar measures.
