OL,3,CCalls from the Channel Islands to
OL,4,Callow bluefin tuna fishing
OL,6,FAngling journalist Greg Whitehead
OL,7,Fsaid: "We could become one of the best
OL,8,Fbig game fisheries on earth."
OL,10,FHe added: "We'd be mad not to go all
OL,11,Fout to attract some of those anglers
OL,12,Fthat are willing to pay #5,000-#6,000
OL,13,Fa week to fish some of these amazing
OL,14,Ffisheries."
