OL,3,CCalls from the Channel Islands to
OL,4,Callow bluefin tuna fishing
OL,6,FGuernsey's Committee for Economic
OL,7,FDevelopment must first apply to become
OL,8,Fa member of the International
OL,9,FCommission for the Conservation of
OL,10,FAtlantic Tunas (ICCAT) to be able to
OL,11,Fallow recreational or commercial
OL,12,Ffishing.
OL,14,FThe committee has warned that "this
OL,15,Fwill involve compliance and legal work
OL,16,Finvolving officers of the Committee
OL,17,Fand DEFRA."
OL,19,FGuernsey Nature Commission are calling
OL,20,Ffor a cautious approach to allowing
OL,21,Ffishing of the species again.
