OL,3,CCalls from the Channel Islands to
OL,4,Callow bluefin tuna fishing
OL,6,FAngela Salmon from the Commission
OL,7,Fsaid: "Bluefin Tuna used to be in our
OL,8,Fwaters many many years ago and the
OL,9,Fpopulation was seriously depleted by
OL,10,Foverfishing.
OL,12,F"So I think anything that we do now
OL,13,Fneeds to be with caution so that we
OL,14,Fdon't repeat history."
OL,16,FJersey has been tagging tuna to
OL,17,Fmonitor numbers and are sharing data
OL,18,Fwith the UK, this information could be
OL,19,Fused to try to negotiate a deal to
OL,20,Fallow bluefin tuna to be caught.
