OL,3,CCalls from the Channel Islands to
OL,4,Callow bluefin tuna fishing
OL,6,FThe UK is currently limited to a quota
OL,7,Fof just 65 tonnes of bluefin tuna for
OL,8,F2024.
OL,10,FJersey's Minister for the Environment,
OL,11,FDeputy Steve Luce, says: "We are in a
OL,12,Fprocess of trying to obtain some quota
OL,13,Fto see whether we do catch and release
OL,14,For even catch a few tuna in the future
OL,15,Ffor our fleet to become more
OL,16,Fprofitable."
